Comment: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu rena ii yoru ni kikoeru ame no me.
Comment: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,---------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:24.32,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,What could I keep watching over
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:30.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,with these empty eyes of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:36.24,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:41.00,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,my life for those whom I must protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:45.34,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,He pulled me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:47.56,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep on flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:53.14,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So far away, but I'll never give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:59.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Our unbreakable bond
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:05.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,has begun to entwine with fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:12.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,guiding us to the endless future laid out before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:21.36,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will get all warm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:26.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,A far-off distance.
