Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.70,Nickname Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(195,0)}Nick: Anchan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:44.45,Nickname Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,388)}Mario Minakami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:44.45,Nickname Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,388)}Nick: Mario
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:56.22,Nickname Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,438)}Tadayoshi Tooyama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:56.22,Nickname Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,438)}Nick: Biceps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.97,Nickname Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(274,474)}Mansaku Matsura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.97,Nickname Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(274,474)}Nick: Cauliflower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:18.24,Nickname Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(322,0)}Noburo Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:18.24,Nickname Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(322,0)}Nick: Spoon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.00,Nickname Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(320,438)}Jo Yokosuka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.00,Nickname Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(320,438)}Nick: Joe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.48,Nickname Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(274,432)}Ryuuji Nomoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.48,Nickname Sign2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(274,432)}Nick: Baremoto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.60,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,These six boys started on their path to salvation in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:32.64,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,They have now given each other nicknames.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:36.91,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:38.81,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your guard up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:40.26,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose your range!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:42.31,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.08,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.79,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing around, Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:56.17,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you do that much boxing, you'll never be at his level.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.34,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.43,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Biceps...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.13,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.22,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we stop now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:05.39,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:06.94,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do 20 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:12.23,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of complaining, you should train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.73,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:18.24,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,I won again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:20.64,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.49,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:25.23,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you owe me a total of 200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:26.90,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Spoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:30.63,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,You could use some exercise to gain some muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:33.00,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.70,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,My teeth are the only I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.04,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't tell 'cause I've only used them on Anchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.39,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,But my jaw is three times more powerful than yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.43,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:49.77,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Baremoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.16,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,You are bragging so much about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.52,DefaultTop,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you are faced with a gun or a pistol, you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my head I've survived this world. {meaning hes a fag that prefers to think instead of fight?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you insinuating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know a fucking thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Spoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always looking for an excuse to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get why Baremoto likes the outside world that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been all alone out there since I was 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never relied on anyone but myself to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I compare this to the outside, this is as if I were in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer being locked here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come from the same place I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you get me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... But..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were not blood related, but we were happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking of Megu is what helps me to stay alive in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I'd like to leave this place soon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and find my sister again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokosuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one that came?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Megu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A visit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, getting a visit from siblings would move anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen a single girl all year that was allowed to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Joe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who came to visit you just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The orphanage director.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She found a family for Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, aren't you happy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what kind of rich family did they find?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, enough, Baremoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe, along with his sister, was abandoned by his mother at the entrance of the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she'd abandoned them at the gates of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, without love, the two kids realized that they could only rely on themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.04,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Safety First
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell you are doing? You've got to move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Line up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next 20 in line, go to the showers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the requested supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you get to your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, the next 20, go i-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A snake!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A snake bit me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a snake around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch it, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:08:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anchan, are you trying to 'scape too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snake is over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, it entered the barracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a venomous one, a venomous snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No I saw it here, it's over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It bit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two boys escaped as fast as they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were aware that if they were caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a fate way worse than dead awaited them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That encouraged them to try even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what motivated Joe the most was the memory of his sister
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which refused to leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They escaped, Ishihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the gravity of the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you only 48 hours to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not able to bring them back within those 48 hours, I'll make sure somebody else does!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should try it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck, those kids sure do run fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Let's go that way! Let's search over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama won't come over today, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that if Megu behaves like a good girl, she will come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Megu will be a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, sing me a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a good singer, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you sing that song for me again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon. Hurry up, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I don't fucking get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to get beaten up for those guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Baremoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only you, but everyone knew we won't get anything out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while knowing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you attracted the attention of the guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to help Joe escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that got you into that isolation cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Spoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, also had a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was always drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did whatever he wanted and he beat us: my mother and my little sister, Tai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was drunk, I always took Tai for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on that August day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went out by myself while my father was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all alone when that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, of all the times I took Tai out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An astounding incandescent flash...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...illuminated for an instant, that summer day, forming a grey mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The houses, the streets, the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister was no where to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how deeply I loved her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have anyone with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Joe has his sister out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he doesn't want to leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why wouldn't I help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect, now that's all settled...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu, from now on, this kind gentleman will be your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pl-please take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now one, we'll be taking care of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy about this, Megu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is your father, so you can rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem quite exhausted. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Megu back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you being just a bit rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone waiting for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help. We'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem. This is for Joe's good as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so rude, Joe. You should be happy that your sister got a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she saw you, she wouldn't be happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, we are done here. Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there you old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing to Megu what you did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just used us as your pleasure toys. What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, perv grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're giving Megu to someone as sick as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just saying stupid things, hurry up and take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not satisfied with us any more, give me back my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!{you great bastard!/you son of a bitch/ lit: fucking abandoned bastard}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, no one would've taken care of you but me. Who don't you show some gratitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fucking joking! You just used the children as you pleased, you perv grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to still say such cruel things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put an end to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to fucking try!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's going to get here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to welcome Joe back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid punk escaped just to find his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to avoid reclusion just for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid people are just stupid after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just wait for him, and hope he doesn't die on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu, Megu. I came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take this guy away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu, don't you get it? They're just using you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director, I'm sorry for the {intromisison}intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu! Don't do it, Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be together,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,waiting for mama to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have I heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come no matter how long we waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were left, forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not blood relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have anyone out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only rely on ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me-Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look for me any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle things myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon. Move your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:20:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megu. What are you doing? Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why many people escape
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to follow a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream which reunites a brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will there be a place in the future where they'll see each other again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this rainy day, the summer was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
